The true art is that which is made naturally, with few interventions. You see it and are completely captivated by its picturesque and marvelous details.
The eyes can see what we desire; we only need to point them in the chosen direction...
But there are some unique directions, those that the Creator, Jehovah, has incredibly planned for human enjoyment and appreciation.
In this collection, the masterful record will belong to Our Perfect Master.

Psalm 19:1-4


A verdadeira arte é aquela feita naturalmente, com poucas intervenções, você vê e fica totalmente atraído aos detalhes pitorescos e maravilhosos.
Os olhos podem ver o que desejarmos, para isso precisamos apenas apontá-los na direção escolhida... 
Mas existem algumas direções únicas, aquelas que o Criador Jeová, planejou incrivelmente para o desfrute e apreciação do ser humano.
Nesta coleção o registro magistral será do Nosso Mestre Perfeito. 
Salmo 19:1-4

collections.name: NeuralTides
collections.description:
I am a digital visionary who reinterprets art in a unique way. My creative journey began on the coasts that have fascinated me since childhood. There, where the waves endlessly crash against the shore, I found inspiration in the harmony between chaos and order.

With my art, I tell stories that lie somewhere between reality and dreams. Each piece is a snapshot that transports viewers to another world – a world filled with emotions, mysteries, and infinite possibilities. I work at the intersection of tradition and the future, blending classical painting with modern digital technology to create timeless works that find their place in the NFT space.

For me, art is not just about aesthetics but about connection – a bridge between artist and collector, between nature and technology. Each piece in my collection carries a message: the search for tranquility, the power of nature, and the value of the moment in an ever-changing world.

collections.description: This NFT is a one-of-a-kind masterpiece, making it truly rare and exceptional.
